               <msContents>
                  <summary>A collection of 3 books on Astronomy.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="WadhMinasian_248-item1" n="1">
                     <locus from="1a" to="15a">ff. 1a-15a</locus>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                     <note type="content-genre">Astronomy</note>
                     <author key="person_f3839">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Sharīf Khātūn'ābādī, Aḥmad bin Muḥammad Mahdī (died 1154 Qamarī/1741).</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">شریف خاتون‌آبادی، احمد بن محمد مهدی (د: ۱۱۵۴ ق/۱۷۴۱م)‏</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" key="work_2972">Maʿrifat taqvīm</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" type="alt" key="work_2972">al-Vajīzah fī Maʿrifat al-Taqvīm</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar" key="work_2972">معرفة تقویم</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar" type="alt" key="work_2972">الوجیزه فی معرفة التقویم</title>
                     <note>This is a treatise on understanding calendars which was written by Khātūn'ābādī upon his friends' request while on a pilgrimage to Karbalā, presented in an introduction and ten chapters, and completed late in Rabīʿ al-avval 1126 Qamarī. Āqā Buzurg has pointed out to this treatise in Al-Zarīʿah (21/250), having written that the author has two works on this topic of which the second in Persian has eight chapters selected from the same work. However, in this treatise Khātūn'ābādī refers to his other books where he has dealt with this topic in more details, hence implying he has other, more comprehensive works on this topic apart from this treatise.</note>
                     <incipit xml:lang="fa">بسمله، حمدله، و بعد چنین گوید اقل عبادالله احمد بن محمد مهدی الشریف الخاتون آبادی این مختصریست مفید در معرفت تقویم مشتمل بر هشت فصل…</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="fa">… کسوف و خسوف که در هر ماهی روی دهد در کنار حاشیهٔ آن نویسند والله اعلم بالصواب بحق النبی المستطاب والسلام.</explicit>
                     <colophon xml:lang="ar">قد فرغ من تسوید هذاه الرساله… حاجی سید حسین خلف… حاجی میر مهدی… فی حین علی البال و اضطراب الاحوال و کان ذلک فی ثانی عشرین من صفر المظفر بعد الف و ماتان ثانی و ثلثون… من سنه ۱۲۳۲ هر که خواند دعا طمع دارم…</colophon>
                     <listBibl>
                        <head>Sequence Number in the Persian Catalogue:</head><bibl>FAW 874</bibl>
                     </listBibl><listBibl><head>Similar copies in other libraries:</head>
